description: Full Metal Minerals Ltd., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Canada. It holds an option to acquire a 60% interest in the Olivine Mountain property located in the Similkameen Mining Division, British Columbia. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Peter  Voulgaris B.E., B.Eng. (Hons), M.Eng.Sci., MAusIMM
